	Conditional Statements:
	To make the set of instructions(block of code)(Conditional bocks) is based on true.
	Used to decide whether the code has to executed or skip based on the given condition.
	Block of code : set of instructions
	It will execute only when the given condition Is true .
	If the condition is true it will executed
